place near here to live.

13:35.448 --> 13:36.616
- Great.

13:36.616 --> 13:39.052
Is a single bedroom
okay for you?

13:39.052 --> 13:40.520
- Yes, single bedroom's fine.

13:40.520 --> 13:42.722
