someone special?

24:26.398 --> 24:28.701
- No, not right now.

24:28.701 --> 24:32.905
I think this will be a
new beginning for me.

24:32.905 --> 24:34.741
I move around too much,

24:34.741 --> 24:37.209
so I never really
have time to settle

24:37.209 --> 24:40.046
and make a connection
with anyone.

24:41.814 --> 24:42.749
- Interesting.

24:42.749 --> 24:45.117
Have you been to lots of places?

24:45.117 --> 24:46.753
- Some places.

24:46.753 --> 24:50.156
I tend to get bored when I
stay in one place too long,

24:50.156 --> 24:52.058
and I like discovering,

24:53.292 --> 24:56.829
discovering people
and places, food.

25:00.399 --> 25:01.668
I better do some studies

25:01.668 --> 25:04.236
because I have a test
in class later today.

25:04.236 --> 25:05.204
Great.

25:05.204 --> 25:06.673
Nice talking to you.

25:06.673 --> 25:08.140
- If you need something,
just come knock on my door.

25:08.140 --> 25:10.577
Of course, yeah.

25:10.577 --> 25:11.410
- Bye.

27:08.294 --> 27:09.962
- Hey, hi, Julie.

27:09.962 --> 27:10.797
What's up?

27:13.666 --> 27:15.067
- You're always in
this little room

27:15.067 --> 27:17.269
in all your spare time.

27:17.269 --> 27:20.873
