you're doing in here.

27:21.741 --> 27:23.710
- I guess it's a hobby of mine.

27:23.710 --> 27:26.212
I like to compose music.

27:26.212 --> 27:27.680
- I didn't know that.

27:27.680 --> 27:29.749
That's really great.

27:29.749 --> 27:33.019
- I'm sorry it's
such a mess in here.

27:33.019 --> 27:34.687
I was gonna try and
fix up my computer,

27:34.687 --> 27:36.355
maybe get a new one.

27:37.990 --> 27:40.760
But hey, do you wanna
see how the stuff works?

27:40.760 --> 27:43.195
- Yeah, yeah, I
would love to see it.

27:43.195 --> 27:45.698
Come on in.

28:48.694 --> 28:51.163
- You are really talented.

28:51.163 --> 28:51.998
Thanks.

28:51.998 --> 28:53.332
You're too kind.

28:58.737 --> 29:00.306
- I should probably go.

29:00.306 --> 29:03.810
You got so much
creative stuff to do.

29:03.810 --> 29:06.112
- Don't worry about it.

29:06.112 --> 29:07.780
- I'll see you later.

29:07.780 --> 29:08.614
Bye.

29:12.718 --> 29:14.020
Thanks for showing me.

29:14.020 --> 29:15.587
I'll see you later.

30:39.005 --> 30:39.838
- Oh, hi.

30:40.706 --> 30:41.540
- Hey.

30:43.175 --> 30:44.376
Are you okay?

30:44.376 --> 30:47.613
- Yeah, I'm just a little tired.

30:47.613 --> 30:49.081
- Yeah.

30:49.081 --> 30:51.283
Is something bothering you?

30:51.283 --> 30:52.518
- Yeah.

30:52.518 --> 30:55.554
I've been talking to
my mom on the internet.

30:55.554 --> 30:58.390
Sorry if I get a
little emotional.

30:59.625 --> 31:01.060
I really miss her.

31:03.062 --> 31:03.996
- I know.

31:03.996 --> 31:06.565
I can understand how that feels.

31:07.699 --> 31:09.969
Why don't you go visit her?

31:12.138 --> 31:15.407
- Actually, I've been
thinking about that,

31:15.407 --> 31:17.977
just see how she's doing.

31:17.977 --> 31:19.478
Why not?

31:20.913 --> 31:22.982
- I've just been
worrying about Michael,

31:22.982 --> 31:24.883
because no one's gonna
take care of him.

31:24.883 --> 31:26.652
- He will be fine.

31:26.652 --> 31:27.786
He's big boy.

31:27.786 --> 31:29.155
He can take care of himself.

31:30.957 --> 31:32.891
- I guess you're right.

31:32.891 --> 31:34.526
Yeah, he's a big boy.

31:36.228 --> 31:37.863
I'm sorry I have to say this.

31:37.863 --> 31:39.999
- Oh, no, no, don't be.

31:39.999 --> 31:42.434
Glad I can help you.

31:42.434 --> 31:44.203
- Thank you, Oxana.

31:44.203 --> 31:45.137
You're so sweet.

32:17.769 --> 32:19.438
- Hey, honey.

32:19.438 --> 32:21.007
Is there something wrong?

32:21.007 --> 32:23.342
You've been quiet all night.

32:25.777 --> 32:26.945
Hey.

32:26.945 --> 32:27.779
Tell me.

32:28.680 --> 32:30.916
Is something bothering you?

32:39.225 --> 32:40.059
- Honey.

32:40.926 --> 32:43.862
I hope you understand this.

32:43.862 --> 32:46.965
I appreciate everything
you have done,

32:46.965 --> 32:49.968
and I'm really happy
being with you,

32:51.537 --> 32:52.371
but

32:54.040 --> 32:56.675
it's just this loneliness.

32:56.675 --> 32:58.410
It's too much for me.

33:01.047 --> 33:04.216
It's just so
overwhelming, everything.

33:05.117 --> 33:07.219
I can't stand it anymore.

33:12.358 --> 33:16.195
- I can't imagine how
hard it must be for you.

33:18.730 --> 33:22.468
Hey, why don't you go
back home for a while

33:22.468 --> 33:24.303
and visit your mother?

33:33.312 --> 33:34.146
Really?

33:35.714 --> 33:36.982
You don't mind?

33:38.584 --> 33:39.885
- Not at all.

33:39.885 --> 33:42.788
I think it'll be good for you.

33:42.788 --> 33:45.091
We can think of it
as a little vacation

33:45.091 --> 33:47.025
away from our marriage.

33:53.132 --> 33:55.401
- You're so silly, Michael.

34:00.206 --> 34:02.808
Do you know how much I love you?

34:06.578 --> 34:08.914
You don't understand.

34:08.914 --> 34:10.416
- I do understand.

34:11.617 --> 34:14.286
I want you to have a great time,

34:16.722 --> 34:19.391
