35:48.680 --> 35:49.515
- I don't know.

35:49.515 --> 35:51.517
Is it strange?

35:52.784 --> 35:54.953
because it's summer.

35:54.953 --> 35:57.489
- I guess it is
a little strange,

35:57.489 --> 35:58.990
but I like this fire.

36:17.409 --> 36:18.910
- Yeah, of course,

36:20.279 --> 36:24.483
but it's nice giving myself
a moment to be alone.

36:28.254 --> 36:30.622
- As strange as it sounds,

36:30.622 --> 36:33.024
I have this sense of freedom.

36:35.627 --> 36:39.631
I haven't slept alone
since we've moved in here.

36:40.499 --> 36:42.901
Now it just suddenly feels like

36:42.901 --> 36:46.238
I don't have to worry
about her anymore.

36:48.407 --> 36:49.641
- It's strange.

36:51.042 --> 36:52.811
Should I let you be then?

36:52.811 --> 36:54.780
- Oh no, I didn't
mean it like that.

36:54.780 --> 36:55.781
Feel free to stay.

37:06.492 --> 37:07.893
I hope you don't mind me saying,

37:07.893 --> 37:09.961
but you look really nice.

37:12.030 --> 37:16.201
- I guess it must be
the fire.

37:17.569 --> 37:20.872
- What do you like to do
during your free time?

37:20.872 --> 37:22.874
- It depends on my mood.

37:24.109 --> 37:27.346
- What about when you
have a lonely mood?

37:30.148 --> 37:32.384
- I write down my thoughts.

37:32.384 --> 37:34.119
In a diary?

37:34.119 --> 37:36.788
- No, not really, just thoughts,

37:37.956 --> 37:40.459
and then I burn
them right after.

37:41.393 --> 37:42.561
You don't like to keep them?

37:44.029 --> 37:48.334
I don't trust myself enough
to keep secrets around.

37:48.334 --> 37:49.535
What if I die

37:49.535 --> 37:52.137
and people go through my stuff

37:52.137 --> 37:57.042
and they're gonna find
out I'm a freak

37:57.042 --> 37:59.177
- You're a private
person, I suppose.

37:59.177 --> 38:00.178
- Yes, I am.

38:02.013 --> 38:06.017
Another thing I sometimes do
is a deep breathing exercise.

38:06.017 --> 38:09.488
It can really help you to sleep.

38:10.456 --> 38:11.523
I could use something like that.

38:11.523 --> 38:13.024
- Yeah, of course.

38:14.059 --> 38:15.727
This is how I do it.

38:18.229 --> 38:21.166
You'll want to relax
your shoulders,

38:21.166 --> 38:22.401
and then you start from here.

38:30.609 --> 38:31.577
Your turn.

38:37.649 --> 38:39.117
Yeah, very good.

38:39.117 --> 38:42.421
Now you just need to be
more fluid and more relaxed.

38:50.328 --> 38:51.162
You see?

38:53.632 --> 38:56.702
Watching you do it
relaxes me already.

38:56.702 --> 39:00.205
- Then I guess it's
time to say goodnight.

39:01.172 --> 39:02.273
- Goodnight, Oxana.

39:02.273 --> 39:03.609
Thanks for all your help.

39:03.609 --> 39:04.510
Of course.

40:10.408 --> 40:11.409
- All right.

40:25.557 --> 40:27.058
Hey, are you okay?

40:28.226 --> 40:29.360
- Yeah, I'm fine.

40:29.360 --> 40:30.195
Why?

40:31.396 --> 40:32.898
- I don't know, man.

40:32.898 --> 40:34.299
It seems like you've been
distracted all morning.

40:35.133 --> 40:36.401
No, I'm fine.

40:37.636 --> 40:39.037
- Yeah, I'm sure.

40:40.438 --> 40:41.439
- All right.

40:42.941 --> 40:43.742
So lunch?

40:45.176 --> 40:46.678
- Yeah, of course.

40:48.980 --> 40:51.249
Fast food, ramen, pad Thai?

40:55.521 --> 40:58.289
Why don't we try
something different today?

41:08.033 --> 41:11.603
You're right, this is
kind of refreshing.

41:11.603 --> 41:14.439
It's a little warm,
but it's nice.

41:15.907 --> 41:17.809
- Isn't it interesting how
you can discover something

41:17.809 --> 41:20.579
you didn't know
was there before?

41:21.613 --> 41:23.081
- Yeah, I guess.

41:32.924 --> 41:35.093
Hey, are you sure
you're okay today?

41:35.093 --> 41:36.762
You're acting weird.

41:38.630 --> 41:40.231
No, I'm fine.

41:40.231 --> 41:41.833
- You don't have to
stress it or anything,

41:41.833 --> 41:45.136
but you can talk
to me about things.

41:45.136 --> 41:46.805
- No really, I'm fine.

41:46.805 --> 41:48.373
Anyways, I think we should
get back to the office.

41:48.373 --> 41:51.042
- Wait wait wait, hold up.

41:51.042 --> 41:52.443
Something is up.

41:52.443 --> 41:53.879
Come on, man, spit it out.

41:53.879 --> 41:55.346
- Really, there's
really nothing.

41:55.346 --> 41:57.683
- Come on, man, spit it out!

41:59.651 --> 42:00.619
- All right.

42:02.287 --> 42:03.354
Have you ever

42:04.823 --> 42:07.993
unexpectedly fantasized
about someone?

42:11.663 --> 42:13.665
- Just like I asked you.

42:15.066 --> 42:18.269
- Yeah, sure, I
fantasize about it.

42:18.269 --> 42:21.272
I fantasize about
it all the time,

42:21.272 --> 42:23.909
but what's the unexpected part?

42:23.909 --> 42:28.647
- I didn't expect to be
fantasizing about this person.

42:32.851 --> 42:34.586
- One of my tenants.

42:39.758 --> 42:41.860
- She's really different.

42:43.762 --> 42:46.031
It's making me
really uncomfortable.

42:46.031 --> 42:49.467
I thought people only
fantasized when they were bored,

42:49.467 --> 42:51.436
and I'm not bored.

42:51.436 --> 42:54.572
- I don't think it
works that way, man.

42:54.572 --> 42:57.976
I think you can fantasize
whenever you want.

42:57.976 --> 43:01.780
It's not like you
cheated on your wife.

43:01.780 --> 43:02.614
Wait, did you?

43:02.614 --> 43:04.149
- No.

43:04.149 --> 43:06.484
- Then you're all good, man.

43:06.484 --> 43:07.753
Fantasize away.

43:09.220 --> 43:10.656
What's confusing?

43:13.258 --> 43:14.760
- Have you ever
been in a situation

43:14.760 --> 43:19.097
where you read this quote
and you say to yourself,

43:19.097 --> 43:21.099
"Yeah, that's my motto,"

43:22.300 --> 43:25.603
but then later you
read another quote

43:25.603 --> 43:28.774
and it's equally as
powerful and inspiring,

43:28.774 --> 43:29.941
and then you're just confused

43:29.941 --> 43:32.644
as to what your motto should be?

43:33.544 --> 43:35.546
Are you serious?

43:36.782 --> 43:40.051
- That's the weirdest
analogy I've ever heard.

43:41.687 --> 43:45.623
- You just compared women
to inspirational quotes.

43:45.623 --> 43:47.525
Who does that?

43:47.525 --> 43:50.729
Look, I can understand
comparing women to cars

43:50.729 --> 43:52.664
or your favorite food,

43:52.664 --> 43:55.967
but inspirational quotes,
that's just weird.

43:55.967 --> 43:58.103
- I don't know, it's
the best I can do.

43:58.103 --> 43:59.705
Anyways, never mind.

43:59.705 --> 44:03.308
- No, look, I'm not
judging you or anything.

44:05.510 --> 44:07.846
I've never heard
that one before.

44:07.846 --> 44:10.248
That must be a oriental thing.

44:10.248 --> 44:11.549
Shut up.

44:11.549 --> 44:13.318
- No, I'm serious, man.

44:13.318 --> 44:15.887
Look, I'm just joking.

44:15.887 --> 44:18.356
I've never heard
that one before.

44:18.356 --> 44:20.992
You're just gonna have to watch
yourself a little bit, okay?

44:20.992 --> 44:22.160
- Yeah, I know that.

44:22.160 --> 44:24.029
With Lily gone and
these two under my roof,

44:24.029 --> 44:27.298
I have to watch
myself constantly,

44:27.298 --> 44:29.000
and you know I'm not like that.

44:29.000 --> 44:30.268
- Yeah, I know
you're not like that,

44:30.268 --> 44:31.937
but I'm just saying,

44:34.740 --> 44:37.175
you never know
when it'll strike.

44:39.477 --> 44:41.246
- The perfect moment.

44:43.915 --> 44:47.152
The moment when the
only thing stopping you

44:47.152 --> 44:49.755
is your own willpower,

44:49.755 --> 44:53.091
and that willpower can
go either way, man.

44:53.091 --> 44:54.826
I'm just saying,

44:54.826 --> 44:58.797
that moment is the
hardest thing to face.

44:58.797 --> 45:01.399
It's like you find a bag of cash

45:02.667 --> 45:05.003
just lying in the
middle of nowhere.

45:05.003 --> 45:06.104
Are you gonna do the right thing

45:06.104 --> 45:08.306
or are you gonna take it?

45:08.306 --> 45:09.741
- Lunch is over.

45:09.741 --> 45:11.642
Let's go back.

45:11.642 --> 45:13.979
- All right, it's your call.

46:01.592 --> 46:03.895
Julie.

46:03.895 --> 46:04.996
Why did
you do that to me?

46:04.996 --> 46:06.731
Julie.

46:06.731 --> 46:07.665
Julie.

46:11.036 --> 46:12.437
I worked so hard.

46:13.338 --> 46:14.272
Julie.

46:14.272 --> 46:16.107
- You just leave me like this.

46:22.413 --> 46:23.248
- Julie.

46:27.953 --> 46:28.786
Julie.

46:31.722 --> 46:32.991
Julie, wake up.

46:36.694 --> 46:37.528
What happened?

46:37.528 --> 46:38.363
Are you okay?

46:38.363 --> 46:39.797
Did you get hurt?

46:42.100 --> 46:42.934
- Yeah.

46:44.669 --> 46:47.605
Yeah, Michael, my
heart is hurting.

46:51.009 --> 46:52.343
He broke it off.

46:53.444 --> 46:55.881
After three years together.

46:55.881 --> 47:00.051
He just couldn't handle
the long distance anymore.

47:07.725 --> 47:08.659
I'm so sad.

47:10.595 --> 47:12.763
I can't focus on anything.

47:13.598 --> 47:16.301
I don't know what to do.

47:16.301 --> 47:18.203
- Don't worry.

47:18.203 --> 47:19.938
Things will get better.

47:19.938 --> 47:22.373
Hey, you're a strong woman,

47:22.373 --> 47:24.542
and you're going to
get through this.

47:26.011 --> 47:27.913
Yeah, I know so.

47:27.913 --> 47:28.746
Trust me.

47:29.680 --> 47:31.782
- Thank you, Michael.

47:31.782 --> 47:33.018
You're so nice.

47:34.652 --> 47:36.654
You're so nice, Michael.

47:38.189 --> 47:40.458
- Let's get you
some water, okay?

47:40.458 --> 47:42.393
And then you can go to bed.

47:42.393 --> 47:43.895
I'm gonna get a cup.

47:43.895 --> 47:46.731
- Michael Michael Michael
Michael Michael Michael,

47:46.731 --> 47:47.565
don't go.

47:47.565 --> 47:48.799
Make me feel good.

47:48.799 --> 47:50.936
Make me feel good,
Michael, please.

47:50.936 --> 47:52.603
Make me feel good.

47:52.603 --> 47:54.839
Please make me
feel good, Michael.

47:54.839 --> 47:56.641
Make me feel good.

47:56.641 --> 47:58.509
Make me feel good, Michael.

47:58.509 --> 48:00.711
Michael, make me feel good.

48:01.846 --> 48:03.348
Make me feel good.

48:04.682 --> 48:05.516
Michael.

48:06.551 --> 48:09.420
Will you make me feel good?

48:09.420 --> 48:12.423
Michael, make me
feel good, Michael.

48:14.325 --> 48:16.594
Make me feel good, Michael.

48:16.594 --> 48:18.997
- Here, why don't you sit up.

48:21.967 --> 48:23.701
All right, come here.

48:25.036 --> 48:28.239
All right, take
deep breaths, okay,

48:28.239 --> 48:29.340
deep breaths.

48:31.676 --> 48:33.644
Just think about your breathing.

51:49.707 --> 51:50.541
- Yeah.

52:13.398 --> 52:16.000
I didn't think I hear anything.

52:17.302 --> 52:19.570
- I was playing in silence.

52:21.672 --> 52:23.908
I didn't wanna wake anyone.

52:30.181 --> 52:33.251
I want to know what
you were playing.

52:34.885 --> 52:37.388
- Yeah, but it's gonna
be really quiet because--

52:37.388 --> 52:40.891
- Oh no no, it's okay,
you can play in silence.

52:40.891 --> 52:44.662
I can follow the keys
and hear it in my head.

53:43.421 --> 53:45.823
I saw what you did for Julie.

53:46.691 --> 53:48.293
That was very nice.

53:50.961 --> 53:54.131
- I'm really not
that much of a saint.

53:56.901 --> 53:59.904
You have proven
something with this.

54:02.039 --> 54:06.043
- Maybe it was more just
a matter of preference.

54:13.518 --> 54:15.353
You're not gonna believe this,

54:15.353 --> 54:16.954
even if I tell you.

54:23.093 --> 54:23.894
- Try me.

54:32.703 --> 54:35.039
It's okay, you can trust me.

54:36.173 --> 54:39.243
Besides, nobody else is here.

54:39.243 --> 54:40.345
It's just us.

54:49.554 --> 54:51.889
- I had a fantasy about you.

54:59.630 --> 55:00.998
Yeah.

55:03.267 --> 55:04.101
- Tell me.

55:11.942 --> 55:12.877
- At first,

55:14.111 --> 55:17.715
I was running my fingers
through your hair,

55:19.650 --> 55:23.253
and then along your
face, across your body.

55:34.031 --> 55:36.367
- Then you get closer to me,

55:37.568 --> 55:40.638
and I feel your lips
with my fingertips.

55:50.247 --> 55:51.749
- Not a whole lot.

56:00.691 --> 56:03.594
- I want to know
what that is like.

56:08.332 --> 56:10.635
I want to experience
your fantasy.

57:09.660 --> 57:11.428
Is this what you saw?

57:20.004 --> 57:22.507
- It's really cold out,

57:22.507 --> 57:24.709
and it's getting late.

57:24.709 --> 57:26.010
I think you should go to bed,

57:26.010 --> 57:28.178
and I'm gonna do the same.

57:32.583 --> 57:34.519
- Good night, Michael.

57:34.519 --> 57:35.586
- Good night.

58:59.436 --> 59:01.639
Wait, maybe we should stop,

59:03.440 --> 59:05.242
before it's too late.

