- Harder.

01:00:14.779 --> 01:00:16.346
- I don't wanna hurt you.

01:00:16.346 --> 01:00:18.548
- That's okay, I want you to.

01:00:34.699 --> 01:00:35.900
You're so sweet.

01:00:35.900 --> 01:00:36.801
Look at me.

