- Hey!

01:04:44.148 --> 01:04:46.016
- Jeez, Dale, what's
wrong with you?

01:04:46.016 --> 01:04:49.119
- Sorry, man, you
forgot these files.

01:04:52.156 --> 01:04:52.990
- Yeah.

01:04:52.990 --> 01:04:53.924
- Thanks.

01:04:54.658 --> 01:04:55.725
Are you okay?

01:04:58.095 --> 01:04:59.529
What gives, man?

